text: Nikita Chandak () (born 5 September 1995) in Urlabari, Nepal is a Nepali model and the title winner of Miss Nepal 2017. She has also won the Miss Popular Choice and Miss Confident titles."निकिता चन्दक भइन मिस नेपाल वर्ल्ड २०१७" SancharNepal.com. Retrieved 3 June 2017. She also represented Nepal at Miss World 2017 pageant which was held in China. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models Category:Miss Nepal winners
